          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-column">
          <h3 class="section-title">Meet
            <span class="highlight">BCG #01</span>
            Winner!</h3>
          <p class="section-text">
            Say hello to our
            <b>BCG #01 winner</b>
            — a passionate community member whose life has just changed forever! In this exclusive interview, he shares his excitement, his journey, and what it feels like to win the car of his dreams.
          </p>
